    {
      "id": "68f8aeb30000000000cb6c50",
      "text": "[*****-() [歓迎.icon]]いらっしゃい！[suto3.icon][ぬね.icon][RR.icon][zatto.icon][meganii.icon][Hiro Aki.icon][nomadoor.icon][基素.icon][seibe.icon][koyoshi.icon][sta.icon][はるひ.icon][wogikaze.icon][cak.icon][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1761128116,
      "updated": 1772399410
    },
    {
      "id": "68f8aeb50000000000cb6c51",
      "text": "\tよろしくお願いします！[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1761128117,
      "updated": 1761128224
    },
    {
      "id": "699d1f480000000000d4cf65",
      "text": " [/customize]でよく見かけた方だ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771904841,
      "updated": 1771904845
    },
    {
      "id": "699d1f4c0000000000d4cf66",
      "text": "  [/customize]だったはず",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771904846,
      "updated": 1771904856
    },
    {
      "id": "699d1f560000000000d4cf67",
      "text": "  ここにいらっしゃる前にどこかのscrapboxで見覚えがあった",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771904856,
      "updated": 1771904874
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a66100000000002d475e",
      "text": " なるほど。自分[Nrem.icon]もtakkerさんのことは[/customize]でよく見かけたような気がします。というか現在進行形でtakkerさんのUserScriptにお世話になってますね…",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772398177,
      "updated": 1772399529
    },
    {
      "id": "69a588e3000000000035448f",
      "text": "   ありがたや[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772456163,
      "updated": 1772456166
    },
    {
      "id": "69a588e60000000000354490",
      "text": "   最近めっきりメンテしてないなんとかしたい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772456166,
      "updated": 1772456185
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4abba00000000005779e8",
      "text": " \t私は結構感情的なので語気が荒くなることがあります。ご迷惑をおかけします",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772399547,
      "updated": 1772399609
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4ab9d00000000005779e7",
      "text": " \tどうぞよろしくお願いします",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772399517,
      "updated": 1772399539
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5887200000000004af5f7",
      "text": " \tよろしくです[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772456050,
      "updated": 1772456057
    },
